  "texts": [
    "First, we aim to determine whether the tutor bot adheres to the long and detailed prompt script, and conversely, if the learner follows the enacted tutor prompt.",
    "Second, we are interested in instances where the tutor bot, acting as a more knowledgeable tutor, introduces new information to the student.",
    "Third, we will examine situations in which the student deviates significantly from the expected path and whether the tutor bot can detect these deviations.",
    "Fourth, given the inaccuracies that ChatGPT is known for, we will assess whether the tutor bot provides incorrect information (hallucinations).",
    "Appendix 1 shows a full transcript of a student's interactions with the tutor bot, a brief analysis of how the interactions are aligned with the PL levels, and a description of how the pre-and post-summaries are scored according to a rubric."
